{"tid":1584941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[習思廣益] 如何善用身邊資源抗爭？","createTime":"2019-09-21T11:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T11:47:16.000Z","uid":129622,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a5849b90aa028a70c9b2b153eeba88fe54647610","tid":1584941,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:15:07.000Z","msg":"參加完屯門和平大遊行換衫坐車走緊 想打幾隻字<br />\n<br />\n香港人無參軍經驗 更無軍火武器<br />\n大部份用來抗爭既野都只係日用品<br />\n由非抗爭用品變成抗爭用品要經歷好長時間同口耳傳播<br />\n一般分運動用品 家庭用品 街頭建設<br />\n<br />\n運動用品就最早投入戰場<br />\n單車頭盔 泳鏡 浮板等等作為防具<br />\n然後有行山杖 球拍 甚至網球 瑜伽等等作為武器<br />\n<br />\n家庭用品就雨傘 鐵兜 摺櫈 水樽<br />\n街頭建設就磚頭 鐵馬<br />\n<br />\n但實在有好多發揮空間而進步得好慢<br />\n或者有人提出過改變 但一落場無人跟住做<br />\n好似前線最愛既三角鐵馬陣<br />\n一直有人講過三角鐵馬係用來衝擊唔係防守<br />\n要阻擋畜龍衝前 將鐵馬打平放 覆蓋範圍更大 <br />\n中間再放陷阱就更難防避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n火魔法作為防守效果其實唔理想 而且多方面成本高<br />\n魚絲 鐵絲網 玻璃樽 隨手可得 清理難 設置易 效果好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最麻煩係比狗搜身屈你藏有武器 <br />\n當遮都係武器 就要搵更多日常易見既野加入戰場<br />\n唔怕無理頭 丟榴蓮皮又得 射AA膠又得 消防喉入水溝水泥又得 <br />\n<br />\n睇返烏克蘭 可能有當兵經驗<br />\n隨手拎起幾樣普通野就組裝成武器防具<br />\n<br />\n我地文宣方面真係創意無限<br />\n係時候諗下勇武方面有咩新玩法大家試試佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82d3b45fc5fc00b008c2c96ab235a8de13bc3b4","tid":1584941,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"[行動又無人理？] 全球最大親子抗爭活動上線啦！ <strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">#birdfoldingchallenge</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1584614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1584614</a><br />\n摺一隻紙鳥，影相，放上Facebook / Twitter / Instagram，並加上hashtag #birdfoldingchallenge #929globalmarch #929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism，copy呢段文字再tag 5個朋友，就完成！</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYhkXcO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYhkXcO.jpg&h=9b11593e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5e17885dad0ccad9fd31b2db1f1a46507343eb1","tid":1584941,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:16:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3aa32bcfda569af82a78eeef927abe7f57c14ff","tid":1584941,"uid":210074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:17:04.000Z","msg":"整個data base"},{"pid":"6301de23bd63c309e2ab4aba9e5b7afed8a27aae","tid":1584941,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:18:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"60bc8886266d697b4897c8781e0b3c6b90187625","tid":1584941,"uid":40880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:18:58.000Z","msg":"其實前線見到都會識抄<br />\n係前線亮過相, 有效果就ok"},{"pid":"9b6c50ac66488c7145458efd067ca0148db9d3e4","tid":1584941,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5100621dd485d7407cdc954f121478ab1d84a2","tid":1584941,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T11:47:16.000Z","msg":"推"}]}